<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM3.6">
<l>empa rattaral lāroṭuṅ kūṭalaṉ</l>
<l>umpar vāḻvaiyoṉ ṟākak karutilaṉ</l>
<l>tampi rāṉama rarkkaraṅ kanakar</l>
<l>empi rāṉukke ḻumaiyum pittaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I shall not associate with those who do not belong to our Highest One.</l>
<l>I shall not consider as worthy of regard the happy life of the celestials.</l>
<l>[I am] the madman of our Lord, He of Raṅgam, the Lord of the immortals, for all seven births.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
